lead_paragraph: November has not been the kindest month for Arsenal in recent seasons and while their schedule over the next four weeks offers plenty of opportunity to slip up again manager Arsene Wenger is determined to keep his players focused on the present.

headline.print_headline: Arsenal Must Put November Struggles to Bed, Says Wenger
headline.main: Arsenal Must Put November Struggles to Bed, Says Wenger
